类 WrapperPlayServerMultiBlockChange

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class WrapperPlayServerMultiBlockChange
extends AbstractPacket
    Represents a multi-block change.

    See also BlockChangeArray for constructing an array of block changes.

      • getRecordData

        public byte[] getRecordData()
        Retrieve the record data.

        Each record is four bytes, containing the following data:

        Bit mask Width Meaning
        00 00 00 0F 4 bits Block metadata
        00 00 FF F0 12 bits Block ID
        00 FF 00 00 8 bits Y co-ordinate
        0F 00 00 00 4 bits Z co-ordinate, relative to chunk
        F0 00 00 00 4 bits X co-ordinate, relative to chunk
        返回:
        The current Record count

      • setRecordData

        public void setRecordData(byte[] value)
        Set the record data.

        Each record is four bytes. See getRecordData() for more information.

        参数:
        value - - new value.
